ssite Action prioritaire : action importante, hautement b\u00e9n\u00e9fique pour la r\u00e9ussite Action mod\u00e9r\u00e9ment prioritaire : action utile, b\u00e9n\u00e9fique pour la r\u00e9ussite \u2022 Les co\u00fbts ont \u00e9t\u00e9 r\u00e9partis en trois niveaux, selon les valeurs approximatives suivantes : Niveau Co\u00fbt approximatif (euros) Faible : 0 \u2013 1000 Moyen : 1000 \u2013 10 000 \u00c9lev\u00e9 : > 10 000 Ces co\u00fbts n\u00e9cessitent d\u2019\u00eatre revus au d\u00e9but de la mise en \u0153uvre du plan d\u2019action. \u2022 Le plan d\u2019action doit \u00eatre r\u00e9examin\u00e9 tous les trois ans, c.-\u00e0-d.", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "0a9480b1-6b54-4708-ba0a-45671faeb358": {"__data__": {"id_": "0a9480b1-6b54-4708-ba0a-45671faeb358", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.iucn.org/fr/resources/litterature-grise/strategie-et-plan-daction-pour-la-conservation-du-mouflon-manchettes", "Author": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Publisher": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "Strat\u00e9gie et plan d'action pour la conservation du mouflon \u00e0 manchettes (Ammotragus lervia) en Tunisie", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.iucn.org/fr/resources/litterature-grise/strategie-et-plan-daction-pour-la-conservation-du-mouflon-manchettes", "Author": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Publisher": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "75523be63b62c553460b1383045c82f230409394f307f9115258e5423bca31ad"}, "2": {"node_id": "9aba2d82-8339-46bd-b0d8-2172d4ac190f", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.iucn.org/fr/resources/litterature-grise/